        "created_at": "2022-08-25T14:12:51.141Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello everyone,</p>\n<p>I joined to add myself to the long list of people who desire this feature.</p>\n<p>I would like my servers to send me Signal messages instead of emails.</p>\n<p>Ideally, it would be helpful if there was a linux command-line tool (for example: <code>/usr/bin/signal myself \"error message\"</code>) and some kind of library that I can call from various scripting languages like PHP, Python, etc.</p>\n<p>Thank you.</p>",
