        "cooked": "<p>Unfortunately, AsamK/signal-cli also requires a phone number, thus why I posted in this thread.</p>\n<p>I am really surprised that this feature has been requested so much but has been ignored. Is there a particular reason why the devs don‚Äôt want people to use Signal without phone numbers?</p>\n<p>Thank you.</p>",
