        "created_at": "2022-08-25T21:24:35.971Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Maybe Signal actually tries to defeat misusage of their service by requiring a phone number?</p>\n<p>It is a simple and straightforward solution to keep the expected load on Signal‚Äôs infrastructure at a manageable level.</p>\n<p>This might explain why Signal insists on requiring a phone number. I‚Äôm pretty sure that, from a technical viewpoint, making phone numbers optional wouldn‚Äôt be a big deal. Other messengers (e.g. Threema) managed to implement this.</p>",
